          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1647964988681-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel your <strong>carrot[s]</strong>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of carrot ribbons</p><p>Peel lengths off your <strong>cucumber</strong> until you end up with a pile of cucumber ribbons</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1647965043356-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1647965043356-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
