          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the basa is cooking, combine your <strong>mayo</strong> with the<strong> remaining chopped coriander</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>coriander mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
